title: TeamTreeHouse - Build a Todo List Application with Rails 4
description:
Let's learn Ruby on Rails 4! In this project we'll develop a simple todo list application calledYou'll learn how to create a Rails application, create models. learn associations, and more. By the end of the project, we'll be able to create todo lists, add items to our lists, and edit and mark them complete.

What you'll learn
Ruby
Ruby on Rails
Associations
Validations
Capybara

Extras Information : 
In the distribution there is a video in SD (360p) and HD (720p)
Level : Beginner 
Ruby : 2.0.0 
Ruby on Rails : 4.0.1
